{"id": "1408150115268562974", "channel_id": "1408140948420165632", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "yeah the sheet only has the 4 profile stories, but none of the quotes or in-battle lines (which are fairly important since those are the lines that play in lobby and over the character's head when you enter a battle). Those are actually probably some of the most-seen lines so it'd be good to be able to clean them up since there's a lot of awkward/wrong ones", "timestamp": "2025-08-21T18:05:49.644000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408140948420165632", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "awakener lines in general (profile stories/quotes/voicelines)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1410391772894330961", "1404748570871201913", "1412867203514236942"]}
{"id": "1408193037313511548", "channel_id": "1408193037313511548", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "One thing that became quickly apparent as I began working on the Prologue, is that the game sometimes seamlessly loads in a cutscene, which often even mimic the dialogue box placement, but all have text embedded directly to the video.\n\nSince we have no way of editing these lines, I thought maybe we could create a repository of screenshots of the various cutscenes, focusing on sentences that we believe need adjustments or complete rewrites.", "timestamp": "2025-08-21T20:56:23.057000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408193037313511548", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Cutscenes with embedded subtitles!", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1404748570871201913", "1412867203514236942"], "is_thread_starter": true}
