{"id": "1408118458364854472", "channel_id": "1408095995535032400", "type": 0, "author_id": "247370231821893632", "author_name": "reapersakamaki", "author_bot": false, "content": "Names usually aren't translated, if the language use another 'alphabet' and lacks a sound that would make it 'normal' it is just adapted this happens a lot, so in my opinion the name itself won't change.", "timestamp": "2025-08-21T16:00:02.050000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408095995535032400", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Name translations", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867280844357813"]}
{"id": "1408091523026911343", "channel_id": "1408091523026911343", "type": 0, "author_id": "899814369926471750", "author_name": "shiio4870", "author_bot": false, "content": "May I see how you do it? I think I need to change my working strategy for this one because I think mine is not efficient enough..\n\nthank you", "timestamp": "2025-08-21T14:13:00.165000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408091523026911343", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Does anyone already did a language translation (that is not EN) ?", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867280844357813"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1408119912488243322", "channel_id": "1408091523026911343", "type": 19, "author_id": "247370231821893632", "author_name": "reapersakamaki", "author_bot": false, "content": "Just some tips and pointers would be:\n\n-Do not change the context of a sentence \n-Do not change the connotation of a sentence\n-Be careful when changing a word to a synonym, as the connotation very often changes\n-Always check who’s speaking. Different people speak differently\n-Do not add unnecessary things. We are adapting and iterating a work, not creating something entirely new", "timestamp": "2025-08-21T16:05:48.740000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["899814369926471750"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "celestepray", "emoji_id": "1397414070100951110", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1408091523026911343", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408091523026911343", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Does anyone already did a language translation (that is not EN) ?", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867280844357813"]}
